---
title: Thai Inspired Chicken Breast and Noodle Stir-Fry with Carrot Ribbons, Sugar Snaps and Sesame Seeds
description: This Thai Inspired Chicken and Noodle Stir-Fry is a crowd pleaser and is one to get the family round the dinner table for. Super simple to make, and easily customised to suit the kids too.
